title: Mortal Kombat 1 Omni-Man vs Scorpion High Level Gameplay
description:
Today during the Kombat Kast we got to see a high level match between Omni-Man and Scorpion by the QA Testers at NetherRealm Studios. Check out the intense action!

title: Mortal Kombat 1 Omni-Man and Tremor Gameplay Overview
description:
Today on the Kombat Kast we got to learn more about Omni-Man's various moves, some combos and his fatal blow. Additionally, we learned more about Tremor as a kameo character including his three variations you can switch between during the match: Metallic, Crystaline, and Aftershock.

title: 5 Reasons To Play Persona 5 Tactica
description: Brought to you by SEGA. It’s time to wake up, get up, and get out there, as the Phantom Thieves are back for a brand new adventure in Persona 5 Tactica. Taking place in all-new locations, featuring some familiar faces as well as some new ones, there’s plenty to dig into when the game launches on November 17th.
